DEMONSTRATION VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KKsfyrx1an4

SETTING UP YOUR DISCORD KEY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to use the mailman bot, you must first create a .env file within the local folder to save your discord token (key) in the following format:

DISCORD_TOKEN={discord token}  # The default key should be working 
							   # Add Salared#1601 on Discord for a new key when malfunctioning


SETTING UP YOUR NEWS API KEY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to generate a free key to use the news api, go to newsapi.org and create an account to a key. Save this key in the .env file in the following format

NEWSAPI_KEY={newsapi key}


RUNNING  THE  BOT
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to run the bot, execute the bot.py file using python3


ACCESSING USER COMMANDS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    !whatsnew - Sends a fresh dose of mail to you right away

    !automail - Enables / disables automatic time-interval mail packets

    !mailsize [number] - set the size of your mail packets

    !interval [1h / 3h / 6h / 12h / 24h] - Set the time-interval between automatic mail packets

    !listcategories - list your personal mail categories

    !addcategory [category] - Add a keyword of interest to your category list

    !removecategory [category] - Remove a category from your personal category list

    !help - List the commands to use this bot

    !options - Open up an interactive menu to edit personal settings
